The '''Drev'starn Spaceport''' was the main [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] in [[Drev'starn]], [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. A mountain plain was expanded and leveled to house the planet's largest starport, not only for practical purposes, but also as a display of prestige. Companies and individuals who could afford to maintain holdings and residents in the expensive districts surrounding the starport gained an instant boost in prestige. Few other [[Species/Legends|species]] placed a premium value on land near a noisy spaceport, but to the enterprising [[Bothan/Legends|Bothans]], the thundering roar of arriving and departing spaceliners symbolized an intimate connection with [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], and, by extension, its many information networks.

